| 802.11 (Wi-Fi) | * -1997 * legacy mode \"IEEE 802.11 (legacy mode)\") * a * b * c * d * e * f * g * h * i * j * k * **n** (Wi-Fi 4) * p * r * s * u * v * w * y * z * aa * **ac** (Wi-Fi 5) * ad (WiGig) * ae * af * ah * ai * aj * ak * aq * **ax** (Wi-Fi 6) * ay * az * ba * bb * bc * bd * **be** (Wi-Fi 7) * bf * bh * bi\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"e73e919c47466ce6\">>>","score":0.82782817},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"ca83e65372e5fed3\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nWireless Connectivity and High Throughput WLAN ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"ca83e65372e5fed3\">>>","url":"https://docs.alltest.net/manual/Alltest-Agilent-Keysight-89601EVMC-TechnicalOverview-30607-.pdf","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"c0b1c7512742e855\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nDesigners can now gain greater insight into the latest wireless LAN signals with the 89600 VSA software for 802.11n/ac/ax, and 802.11be modulation analysis.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"c0b1c7512742e855\">>>","score":0.7233095}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774961748403}}
{"type":"message","id":"1eae9869","parentId":"dd01f279","timestamp":"2026-03-31T12:56:00.872Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"从搜索结果看：\n1. DCM 可以使用 BPSK、QPSK 和 16-QAM\n2. 在 802.11ax 中，DCM 主要用于 BPSK 和 coding rate 1/2，定义了 MCS 14 和 MCS 15\n\n让我获取更详细的信息，特别是 EHT 中 DCM 的具体规定。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_834afce6c8604fa78af2557a","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/dual-carrier-modulation-dcm-wi-fi-unlocking-through-yash-k-saxena-rsjic","extractMode":"markdown"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":51420,"output":200,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51620,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774961748404,"responseId":"9645e84b06f7c529c11f73a6541872d7"}}
