{"type":"message","id":"7ab8eca8","parentId":"1e8155ad","timestamp":"2026-03-31T16:07:36.020Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要创建验证知识库和设计知识库的目录结构（预留），然后清理工作空间根目录的临时文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_cf95ae63c6a442d493ad71a9","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 验证知识库\n\n> 芯片验证方法学、UVM、覆盖率、断言等\n\n---\n\n## 📚 知识索引\n\n### 一、验证方法学\n\n| 主题 | 文件 | 关键词 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| 待补充 | - | UVM, OVM, VMM |\n\n### 二、验证策略\n\n| 主题 | 文件 | 关键词 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| AI 时代的验证 | [ai_verification.md](./ai_verification.md) | AI 写 RTL, 验证策略转变 |\n\n### 三、覆盖率\n\n| 主题 | 文件 | 关键词 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| 待补充 | - | Code Coverage, Functional Coverage |\n\n### 四、断言\n\n| 主题 | 文件 | 关键词 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| 待补充 | - | SVA, Immediate Assertion, Concurrent Assertion |\n\n---\n\n## 🔄 更新记录\n\n| 日期 | 更新内容 |\n|------|---------|\n| 2026-04-01 | 创建验证知识库结构 |\n","path":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace-my_work_robot\\knowledge\\verification\\README.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":63744,"output":324,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64068,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774973235454,"responseId":"0bc444dcc45ab21e0bddeddfb9c02bd3"}}
