{"type":"message","id":"6991494a","parentId":"67303755","timestamp":"2026-03-31T16:08:45.563Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在创建设计知识库的预留目录。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_02daf165810b4c3f87257ff1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 设计知识库\n\n> RTL 设计、架构设计、Verilog/SystemVerilog 设计技巧\n\n---\n\n## 📚 知识索引\n\n### 一、RTL 设计\n\n| 主题 | 文件 | 关键词 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| 待补充 | - | Verilog, SystemVerilog, 时序逻辑 |\n\n### 二、架构设计\n\n| 主题 | 文件 | 关键词 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| 待补充 | - | 流水线, 并行处理, 状态机 |\n\n### 三、低功耗设计\n\n| 主题 | 文件 | 关键词 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| 待补充 | - | Clock Gating, Power Gating, DVFS |\n\n### 四、时钟域交叉\n\n| 主题 | 文件 | 关键词 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| 待补充 | - | CDC, 异步FIFO, 握手协议 |\n\n---\n\n## 🔄 更新记录\n\n| 日期 | 更新内容 |\n|------|---------|\n| 2026-04-01 | 创建设计知识库结构（预留） |\n","path":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace-my_work_robot\\knowledge\\design\\README.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":65518,"output":291,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65809,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774973309312,"responseId":"2a846c26d242eb666354a4f65749e185"}}
